3019710b-b607-4a56-98a4-62b9af1a4eae.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill yellow squares in the hole of the rectangle and also add yellow squares on either all of the horizontal or all of the vertical lines out of the hole.  Then add more yellow squares on a diagonal starting from the inner corner of each hole and going to the edge of the grid.  Some yellow squares will repeat the yellow squares to fill the hole.
3019710b-b607-4a56-98a4-62b9af1a4eae.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid size
3019710b-b607-4a56-98a4-62b9af1a4eae.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 7x7 black grid with a single color of squares that form a rectangle with a black hole

368bea8b-8b4b-4e72-8968-ef3122f0ea30.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill in the pattern with yellow,  color the black squares that make a straight line to the edge of the grid yellow, and create one yellow diagonal line from the line to the edge.
368bea8b-8b4b-4e72-8968-ef3122f0ea30.grid_description: The output grid size...does not change.
368bea8b-8b4b-4e72-8968-ef3122f0ea30.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 7x7black grid with a single color pattern.
